{"tid":380401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印藏部隊強制新兵學中文　盼減不必要衝突","createTime":"2017-08-30T05:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T14:32:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d797e14a1a4c6dc23ab83c363c62a0616ed6bbbf","tid":380401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bknint-20170830095514069-0830_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170830104744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170830095514069-0830_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170830104744&h=04bf96ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n08月30日(三) 09:55<br />\n中印兩國在洞朗地區的對峙暫告一段落。有印媒報道，印藏邊防部隊決定今後招募的新兵，都必須強制學習中文，以免因語言上的誤會，而與中方發生不必要衝突。<br />\n<br />\n《印度快報》周二（29日）報道，一名部隊的高級軍官表示，學習普通話和藏語將成為新兵為期一年的訓練一部分。他解釋指：「我們幾乎每天都要與中國士兵互動，學習中文能有助避免誤會，妥善地解決糾紛。」據悉，駐守於長達3488公里邊界線的9萬名印藏邊防部隊士兵中，只有不足150人略懂中文，但他們亦只能說出大概10句中文。<br />\n<br />\n一名軍官指出，言語上的溝通有助表達個人感受，亦較容易化解分歧，希望計劃能有助減少如早前在班公湖發生的糾紛。據報，部隊已聘請12名老師，目標是讓是整支隊伍，每個人都掌握50至60句中文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bknint-20170830095514069-0830_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fbknint-20170830095514069-0830_17011_001.html&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=aa79f6dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bknint-20170830095514069-0830_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"95c70dcb2a1a0e5e412c1eeb213a67df259ad008","tid":380401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b132d72e208673b0f166ac7d9e289cf77e2523f","tid":380401,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"棋王出招了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb2b7c2bafe4fd5ec5523ed8f6bcf4f70a00d2a","tid":380401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f073a864e4c6b5786becbc1a7ed98e328c4afe","tid":380401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd13b9830b86157727d4ea228d4b6763b537247","tid":380401,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"係咪支那出錢比印度學架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef6a3c551164ec04f2ac2e5002c6fc4f19a9575","tid":380401,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"你老母 呢度係印度呀"},{"pid":"da3fd24cd1b6b3e1075ec65fa31774d1aafe6991","tid":380401,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"第一句:操你媽b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a47198cb624ecb2c5f4e37e516fe54df5cb1fdf","tid":380401,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"聽得明講咩 衝突仲勁"}]}